<div class="container py-3">
  <div class="row ">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 ">
      <%= image_tag(@product.photo_url, width: '100%') %>
      <p><strong>Need help with your MVP?</strong></p>
      <p>- I can customize your product design and add others features.</p>

      <p><strong>Next Functionality:</strong></p>
      <p>- Add a calendar for booking.
      <br />- Add feature for new map.
      <br />- Add feature for credit card.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
      <p class="h4 text-uppercase text-orange">Product Details</p>
      <p class="font-18 text-muted">Get the starter code for your project</p>
      <p>Allow users to browse existing properties, create an account, sign in and post their own properties. Users can visit their own dashboard to see their properties.</p>
      <p><strong>Functionality included:</strong></p>

      <p>- Browse existing properties.
      <br />- Sign up / sign in / forgot password.
      <br />- Upload new properties.
      <br />- User dashboard to view properties.</p>

      <p><strong>About the code:</strong></p>

      <p>- Built with Ruby on Rails 6.
      <br />- Ready to deploy to live website.      
      <br />- Instructions on how to setup included.</p>

      <%= form_tag orders_path do %>
        <%= hidden_field_tag 'product_id', @product.id %>
        <%= submit_tag 'Purchase', class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
      <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


